description: MAGID Gemstone Myst Safety Glasses deliver superior eye protection in a comfortable design. The foam-lined safety glasses offer complete eye protection that successfully merges comfort, performance and savings in style. Offering the same protective qualities as the existing style of Myst Safety Glasses, the Y10FMAFC has an added silver EVA foam-lined lens to cushion and protect against fine particles such as dust, sand, and cement. These safety glasses also feature frosted temples that are sleek and stylish, along with a wraparound frame for maximum protection from every angle. The safety glasses are lightweight and comfortable to wear, making long-term use a possibility. Gemstone Myst Safety Glasses feature a hard-coated polycarbonate lens that meets ANSI Z87.1-2010 High-Impact Safety Standards and blocks approximately 99.9% of harmful ultraviolet light.
